    public final class RingArrayBlockingQueue<E>
extends java.util.AbstractList<E>
implements java.util.concurrent.BlockingQueue<E>

    Represent an expandable blocking/non-blocking FIFO queue backed by a ring buffer. It implements two lock concurrent queue algorithm.

    Author:
    Rishi Gupta
